      <!-- Banner Caption Start --> 
      <div id="banner1" class="nivo-html-caption"> 
       <h1>Event Staffing</h1> 
       <p>Landmark brings an unparalleled team to the operation of each event. We provide this experience and expertise in a unique manner. We are focused on working for the good of your cause in a Client-friendly, Fan-friendly, Employee-friendly manner. Our focus on our employees creates the best possible experience for your guests. </p> 
      </div> 
      <!-- Banner Caption End --> 
      <!-- Banner Caption Start --> 
      <div id="banner2" class="nivo-html-caption"> 
       <h1>Stadiums &amp; Arenas</h1> 
       <p> From ice shows, motocross and major concerts to professional and collegiate football, basketball and hockey, Landmark has proven it will provide top-flight services no matter how big or small the call. Landmark is a leader in both access control and the guest services essential to large events at classic and new venues. </p> 
      </div> 
      <!-- Banner Caption End --> 
      <div id="banner3" class="nivo-html-caption"> 
       <h1 class="smaller">University Athletics &amp; Events</h1> 
       <p> Landmark understands the unique dynamics of university athletics and special events and the varied expectations of students, faculty, donors, alumni and the general public. We provide services both to athletic department and general campus services. </p> 
      </div> 
      <!-- Banner Caption End --> 
      <!-- Banner Caption Start --> 
      <div id="banner4" class="nivo-html-caption"> 
       <h1>Concert Venues</h1> 
       <p> Landmark’s team has provided exceptional services to thousands of concerts over many decades. From small theatres and orchestras to amphitheatres and concert festivals, Landmark has the skill and expertise to handle the unique issues that arise with each type of music event in a manner that takes into account our clients’ needs and goals. </p> 
      </div> 
      <!-- Banner Caption End --> 
      <!-- Banner Caption Start --> 
      <div id="banner5" class="nivo-html-caption"> 
       <h1>Conventions</h1> 
       <p> Attentive guest services are essential at conventions, conferences and meetings. From VIP meetings to major trade shows, Landmark will place the right people in the right position to ensure security that is solid but barely noticeable. </p> 
      </div> 
      <!-- Banner Caption End --> 
      <!-- Banner Caption Start --> 
      <div id="banner6" class="nivo-html-caption"> 
       <h1>Special Events</h1> 
       <p> Landmark excels in providing planning and services for special events. Some of the most prominent conferences, leagues, organizations, festivals and retailers nationwide rely on Landmark for the assurance that their crowd management and security requirements will be met so they can focus on the other aspects of their event. </p> 
