        <h1 class="heading colr">The Landmark Way</h1> 
        <p> It’s your house, and their home away from home. Your guests deserve the best. They deserve more than just respect, they deserve to feel a part of your family. You need to entrust your Guest Experience to an event staffing firm that will ensure the best in a Client-friendly, Fan-friendly, Employee-friendly manner. Landmark Event Staffing Services is the answer. </p>
        <br>
        <p> Landmark is built on a solid foundation designed to serve our clients' needs in a cooperative fashion with their goals in mind. We have decades of experience dealing with every type and issue that might arise. We strive to prevent guest issues before they become a problem, so our clients can focus on the rest of the event. </p> 
